-- Retailer Edcon Appoints Schreiber as New CEO; Ross Will Retire in May 2012
-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 2011-01-28T06:30:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-01-28/retailer-edcon-appoints-schreiber-as-new-ceo-ross-will-retire-in-may-2012.html
Edcon (Pty) Ltd., the South African
retailer owned by Bain Capital LLC, said Jurgen Schreiber will
take over as chief executive officer of the company from April
1.  Current CEO Stephen Ross will retire in May 2012, the
company said in an e-mailed statement today from Johannesburg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  